CalculatedFields.Name: campaign_journey_type
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse({pinpoint_campaign_journey_type} = 'transactional', 'API',
ifelse({event_name} = 'null', 'segment based',
ifelse({event_name} <> 'null', 'event based',
    NULL
)))

CalculatedFields.Name: date_drill_down
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Day', truncDate("DD", {event_timestamp_timezone}), 
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Week', truncDate("WK", {event_timestamp_timezone}), 
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Month', truncDate("MM", {event_timestamp_timezone}), 
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Quarter', truncDate("Q", {event_timestamp_timezone}), 
truncDate("YYYY", {event_timestamp_timezone})
))))

CalculatedFields.Name: date_drill_down
CalculatedFields.Expression:

truncDate("YYYY", {event_timestamp_timezone})
))))

CalculatedFields.Name: date_drill_down
CalculatedFields.Expression:
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Day', truncDate("DD", {event_timestamp}), 
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Week', truncDate("WK", {event_timestamp}), 
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Month', truncDate("MM", {event_timestamp}), 
ifelse(${GroupByTime} = 'Quarter', truncDate("Q", {event_timestamp}), 
truncDate("YYYY", {event_timestamp})
))))
